songs.title: Hey Baby
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Yeah, hey, baby, why you treating me bad?
Hey, darling, you're making me mad
I'm going crazy trying to figure out why you are leaving
Give me a reason

[Pre Chorus]
Say that you need me
I know you're deceiving
The lies that you're feeding will leave you alone

[Chorus]
Please don't ask me to go
I'm already gone, I'm already gone
Please just leave me alone
I'm already gone, I'm already gone
Oh, oh

[Verse 2]
Hey, baby, what's the matter with you?
Hey, darling, know your love isn't true
I'm going crazy trying to figure out why you are leaving
Give me a reason

[Verse 3]
Hey, baby, why you bein' a fool?
Hey, darling, always been good to you
I'm going crazy trying to figure out why you are leaving
Give me a reason

[Pre Chorus]
Say that you need me
I know you're deceiving
The lies that you're feeding will leave you alone

[Chorus]
Please don't ask me to go
I'm already gone, I'm already gone
Please just leave me alone
I'm already gone, I'm already gone
Oh, oh

[Bridge]
Yeah, hey, baby, why you treating me bad?
Hey, darling, you're making me mad
I'm going crazy trying to figure out why you are leaving
Give me a reason

[Pre Chorus]
Say that you need me
I know you're deceiving
The lies that you're feeding will leave you the feeling of misery
Baby, and terrible, scary
I need you to leave me alone

[Chorus]
Please don't ask me to go
I'm already gone, I'm already gone
Please just leave me alone
I'm already gone, I'm already gone
Oh, oh
Hey, baby
